{"tid":736541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係絕對贊成放生害蟲的","createTime":"2018-07-10T10:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T11:09:29.000Z","uid":116471,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9a043930b88e22d37c2112fd1fd43f766bdd8330","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:04:22.000Z","msg":"我們對於螞蟻、蚊蟲、蒼蠅、蟑螂，我們跟牠溝通都是誠誠懇懇像對佛菩薩一樣，合掌禮敬，稱牠菩薩，蟑螂菩薩，螞蟻菩薩，聽話，不能用輕慢心。我們跟牠溝通之後，然後回避，一、兩個小時牠一定都走了，都散掉了。所以跟對人一樣，要尊重，不能夠輕慢，不能夠無禮，也不能夠威脅、要脅，都不可以，要很尊重。牠們到這邊來，當然有很多都是找食物的，我們把食物放在院子裡，放在戶外，供養牠們，會合作的。一切眾生都有靈性，佛說一切眾生都有佛性，一定要用真誠懇切你才能感動這些小動物。在過去我們不懂這個道理，傷害了牠們，我們常常忏悔，我們自己誦經、念佛給牠回向。我們這個佛堂裡面都供養著小畜生的牌位，你們仔細去看看，你就曉得，我們天天不忘記牠們，我們天天感謝牠跟我們的合作。"},{"pid":"920b342a64bae641b7506064a48ca48137e3b8a3","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:05:12.000Z","msg":"應該跟隨我，吃素，愛護所有動物。"},{"pid":"52165d6e10234f70ee88c52891b0c086b3319c7e","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.renegadetribune.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/hitler-deer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.renegadetribune.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fhitler-deer.jpg&h=c87a432f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e6bd18732e1a7fc9b9e43323a645d2018c91259","tid":736541,"uid":64318,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:06:33.000Z","msg":"屌你都費事"},{"pid":"79f61feeaa3213c9369126d4581c63366dc2b1a7","tid":736541,"uid":92690,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"人類先係害蟲"},{"pid":"6d4fff0654e8f3fa65aad525655886cb5c679951","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:07:25.000Z","msg":"世界冥冥中有主宰，我黨之標誌與佛教類似，也不是完全巧合 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de40d83d183d9ad5f7fcd06eb7ed755f0e5fe13f","tid":736541,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:07:36.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"055ebcd9198c05a051c898ed87ddeaeb4ac2fa6f","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"79f61feeaa3213c9369126d4581c63366dc2b1a7","tid":736541,"uid":92690,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"人類先係害蟲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有慧根"},{"pid":"32188ef923daea305b8eab0a2412ba9f54f35707","tid":736541,"uid":101968,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"佛觀一缽水，八萬四千蟲，樓主唔應該飲水"},{"pid":"b3b44e58b8773e43e393c1cd7232dbde16b803e3","tid":736541,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:08:40.000Z","msg":"日日都被放百幾隻害蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c06ff0ee166088c3028e76e43f0edf2b31ed1c6","tid":736541,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"055ebcd9198c05a051c898ed87ddeaeb4ac2fa6f","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"79f61feeaa3213c9369126d4581c63366dc2b1a7","tid":736541,"uid":92690,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"人類先係害蟲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有慧根"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:09:06.000Z","msg":"所以我要啪一啪手指<br />\n世界就和平了"},{"pid":"1191e7bc3abdffe52c1680a7df5b628bfe5d3716","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"32188ef923daea305b8eab0a2412ba9f54f35707","tid":736541,"uid":101968,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"佛觀一缽水，八萬四千蟲，樓主唔應該飲水"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"釋迦牟尼話不知者不罪"},{"pid":"6a2f79d1d323f7e2754016ad6bc6f161116ef45a","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"這位高僧如此描述：希特勒本人，曾經在多個過去世前，是一條海中的魚王。在他所屬的海洋當中，有著眾多的小魚，當時的有許多漁民，以打魚作為行業。<br />\n<br />\n就是希特勒所轄的這些諸多海魚，被當時眾國漁民捕撈。及作為食物。由於這些魚兒在臨死時，發下了很大的誓願：「在將來有機會在投生為人，一定會消滅所有殺過它們，以及把他們作為食物的人」。<br />\n<br />\n不幸的是，當時的這些漁民，後來投生為了猶太人。希特勒之所以掌權後，打算用屠殺的方式，消滅這個種族。他正是當時的魚王，而這其他小魚們就是希特勒手下的將官和士兵。<br />\n<br />\n希特勒有個特點，就是吃素食。並不是他本人善良，而是他過去世當中，生生都是在畜生道投生，一直是動物魚類。因為這樣的自身業力和習氣。所以看到「同類動物」就不敢去吃。<br />\n<br />\n這樣前後的因果，由於過去世當中極大的怨氣願力成熟，才有了後來的第二次世界大戰。及猶太人被滅族的慘劇。"},{"pid":"f8391e7cfceff38de471e8f3836f68b8d5647c26","tid":736541,"uid":56339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1191e7bc3abdffe52c1680a7df5b628bfe5d3716","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"32188ef923daea305b8eab0a2412ba9f54f35707","tid":736541,"uid":101968,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"佛觀一缽水，八萬四千蟲，樓主唔應該飲水"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"釋迦牟尼話不知者不罪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"你依家知啦 拿拿林摺埋收皮啦"},{"pid":"d0f8e2d3d3ca1610c6cf83f4eb297f4a20a180df","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8391e7cfceff38de471e8f3836f68b8d5647c26","tid":736541,"uid":56339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1191e7bc3abdffe52c1680a7df5b628bfe5d3716","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"32188ef923daea305b8eab0a2412ba9f54f35707","tid":736541,"uid":101968,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"佛觀一缽水，八萬四千蟲，樓主唔應該飲水"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"釋迦牟尼話不知者不罪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"你依家知啦 拿拿林摺埋收皮啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"但故意殺害害蟲就唔係咁講法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24142f74ba97a55f7e222ccf2a800275d694b98d","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:17:32.000Z","msg":"所以荃灣普通話男女當街放生曱甴，我係感到十分高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969949b4a9b32bb15855ba1fe7133ed9668bef09","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:18:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0XLdV8tMRyc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0XLdV8tMRyc&d=Tql5HschcrwOX14smS%2Fg%2Bv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=16e36308\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0XLdV8tMRyc</a>"},{"pid":"827fed242f771e059addf5c35b5be668ec400dd6","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZuchqnC1Bog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZuchqnC1Bog&d=Tql5HschcrwOX14smS%2Fg%2Bv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=408d6ded\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZuchqnC1Bog</a>"},{"pid":"8cc11ff939882e73d9d2b568ced0770e62c97841","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uPJZanPnosk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuPJZanPnosk&d=Tql5HschcrwOX14smS%2Fg%2Bv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=19b8727c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uPJZanPnosk</a>"},{"pid":"a62251be5b813121a52990854e9d5c5e94cb03fc","tid":736541,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1191e7bc3abdffe52c1680a7df5b628bfe5d3716","tid":736541,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"32188ef923daea305b8eab0a2412ba9f54f35707","tid":736541,"uid":101968,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"佛觀一缽水，八萬四千蟲，樓主唔應該飲水"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"釋迦牟尼話不知者不罪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0